      <format type="text/markdown"><![CDATA[  
  
## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="f61d5-102"><xref:System.Xml.XmlReader>類別可以使用強制執行驗證的結構描述或文件類型定義 (DTD)。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f61d5-102">The <xref:System.Xml.XmlReader> class can enforce validation using a schema or document type definition (DTD).</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="f61d5-103"><xref:System.Xml.ValidationType>列舉會指定驗證所建立的類型<xref:System.Xml.XmlReader>應該執行的執行個體。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f61d5-103">The <xref:System.Xml.ValidationType> enumeration specifies the type of validation the created <xref:System.Xml.XmlReader> instance should perform.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="f61d5-104"><xref:System.Xml.XmlReader>執行個體可以是任一驗證<xref:System.Xml.XmlReader>所建立的物件<xref:System.Xml.XmlReader.Create%2A>方法，或有<xref:System.Xml.XmlValidatingReader>物件。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f61d5-104">The <xref:System.Xml.XmlReader> instance can be either a validating <xref:System.Xml.XmlReader> object created by the <xref:System.Xml.XmlReader.Create%2A> method, or an <xref:System.Xml.XmlValidatingReader> object.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="f61d5-105">驗證模型具有三個特性，嚴格、 資訊和狀態。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f61d5-105">The validation model has three characteristics, strict, informative, and status.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="f61d5-106">Strict，不允許混合驗證型別，具有資訊價值的提出警告，如果找不到結構描述或文件類型定義 (DTD)，且狀態會提供警告，如果項目和屬性從結構描述無法執行驗證。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f61d5-106">Strict, does not allow the mixing of validation types, informative provides a warning if the schema or document type definition (DTD) cannot be found, and status provides warnings if validation cannot be performed for elements and attributes from schemas.</span></span>  
  
